\p 
\v 1 Naa  čoluma Davide v…Ēnini Filisiti nuiti ma, eŐĀ ti …†aazu unfe se…†e, eŐĀ ta-laa wolai Gate …†ula ti ya, naa  č…õ…õ koba laaiti p…õ ba.
