\v 16 Ayitu…ďe naŐĀ-doun zunui Sad…Ēke, ta A…ďiataal naŐĀ-doun zunui A…ďimel…õke, ti …†…õ ga zala…†a …†ula nuiti, Sav…Ē…†a …†…õ ga s…õ č…õ …†…õ nui.
